{"title":"Nginx部署","uid":"22e976045f79a913a7ea0143ddb4fa7e","slug":"Nginx部署","date":"2023-04-08T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-05-19T17:58:55.775Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Nginx部署.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/medias/1668057369541.png","content":"<h2 id=\"nginx源码\"><a href=\"#nginx源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"nginx源码\"></a>nginx源码</h2><p><strong>官网：</strong><a href=\"http://nginx.org/\">nginx news</a></p>\n<p><strong>源码包：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>下载想要的nginx版本</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/../images/Nginx%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/image-20230404145154624.png\" alt=\"image-20230404145154624\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-源码包下载：\"><a href=\"#1-源码包下载：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.源码包下载：\"></a><strong>1.源码包下载：</strong></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>复制源码包的下载链接</p>\n<p>-P  指定下载包的路径</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;nginx.org&#x2F;download&#x2F;nginx-x.x.x.tar.gz -P &#x2F;usr&#x2F;src   \ncd &#x2F;usr&#x2F;src\nls</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"2-安装依赖包-解压源码\"><a href=\"#2-安装依赖包-解压源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装依赖包,解压源码\"></a>2.安装依赖包,解压源码</h3><h4 id=\"centos\"><a href=\"#centos\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"#centos\"></a><strong>#centos</strong></h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum -y install gcc pcre-devel zlib-devel</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>gcc： 源码编译工具 </li>\n<li>pcre-devel： nginx url_rewrite 功能提供包 </li>\n<li>zlib-devel： nginx 压缩功能提供包</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"ubuntu\"><a href=\"#ubuntu\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"#ubuntu\"></a><strong>#ubuntu</strong></h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt-get -f install    # 自动安装依赖包</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tar -xvf 包名\ncd 包文件夹</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"3-配置nginx源码\"><a href=\"#3-配置nginx源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.配置nginx源码\"></a>3.配置nginx源码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">.&#x2F;configure --prefix&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx </code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>配置目的：</p>\n<p>.&#x2F;configure                            #检查环境 是否 满足安装条件 依赖解决</p>\n<p>–prefix&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx     #指定软件安装在那里</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"4编译、安装-nginx-源码\"><a href=\"#4编译、安装-nginx-源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4编译、安装 nginx 源码\"></a>4编译、安装 nginx 源码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">make &amp;&amp; make install</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"5-启动nginx\"><a href=\"#5-启动nginx\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.启动nginx\"></a>5.启动nginx</h3><p><strong>检查配置文件</strong>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -t</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Nginx启动：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Nginx关闭：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">killall nginx</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>指定配置文件：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -c &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;nginx.conf</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>注意：-c 指定配置文件的路径，不加的话，nginx会自动加载默认路径的配置文件，可以通过 -h查看帮助命令</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"6-查看nginx进程\"><a href=\"#6-查看nginx进程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.查看nginx进程\"></a>6.查看nginx进程</h3><p>使用 netstat 命令查看启动端口 </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">netstat -ano | grep 80</code></pre>\n\n<p>使用losf命令查看启动端口</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">lsof -i :80</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"7-创建软链接\"><a href=\"#7-创建软链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7.创建软链接\"></a>7.创建软链接</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>建立软链接（由于&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin包含于$PATH当中，这样就不需要额外的设置环境变量了，这意味着可以在其他路径下直接运行nginx命令）</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ln -s &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin</code></pre>\n\n<p>在任何目录下启动nginx服务直接输入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nginx</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>不想用这种方法来启动nginx服务的，可以用第8步骤内的方法</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"8-将nginx添加为linux系统服务\"><a href=\"#8-将nginx添加为linux系统服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8.将nginx添加为linux系统服务\"></a>8.将nginx添加为linux系统服务</h3><p><strong>创建配置文件</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vim &#x2F;usr&#x2F;lib&#x2F;systemd&#x2F;system&#x2F;nginx.service\n\n#添加以下内容\n[Unit]\nDescription&#x3D;nginx\nAfter&#x3D;network.target\n  \n[Service]\nType&#x3D;forking\nPIDFile&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;logs&#x2F;nginx.pid\nExecStartPre&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -t -c &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;nginx.conf\nExecStart&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -c &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;nginx.conf\nExecReload&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -s reload\nExecStop&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nginx -s quit\nPrivateTmp&#x3D;true\n  \n[Install]\nWantedBy&#x3D;multi-user.target</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ul>\n<li><p>Unit   </p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Description，服务的描述  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Documentation，文档介绍  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>After，该服务要在什么服务启动之后启动，比如Mysql需要在network和syslog启动之后再启动</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Install   - </p>\n<ul>\n<li>WantedBy，值是一个或多个Target，当前Unit激活时(enable)符号链接会放入&#x2F;etc&#x2F;systemd&#x2F;system目录下面以Target名+.wants后缀构成的子目录中   - </li>\n<li>RequiredBy，它的值是一个或多个Target，当前Unit激活(enable)时，符号链接会放入&#x2F;etc&#x2F;systemd&#x2F;system目录下面以Target名+.required后缀构成的子目录中   - </li>\n<li>Alias，当前Unit可用于启动的别名   - </li>\n<li>Also，当前Unit激活(enable)时，会被同时激活的其他Unit</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Service   </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type，定义启动时的进程行为。它有以下几种值。  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type&#x3D;simple，默认值，执行ExecStart指定的命令，启动主进程   </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type&#x3D;forking，以 fork 方式从父进程创建子进程，创建后父进程会立即退出 </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type&#x3D;oneshot，一次性进程，Systemd 会等当前服务退出，再继续往下执行  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type&#x3D;dbus，当前服务通过D-Bus启动  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type&#x3D;notify，当前服务启动完毕，会通知Systemd，再继续往下执行   </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type&#x3D;idle，若有其他任务执行完毕，当前服务才会运行  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ExecStart，启动当前服务的命令   </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ExecStartPre，启动当前服务之前执行的命令   </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ExecStartPost，启动当前服务之后执行的命令 </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ExecReload，重启当前服务时执行的命令  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ExecStop，停止当前服务时执行的命令  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ExecStopPost，停止当其服务之后执行的命令  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>RestartSec，自动重启当前服务间隔的秒数  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Restart，定义何种情况 Systemd 会自动重启当前服务，可能的值包括always（总是重启）、on-success、on-failure、on-abnormal、on-abort、on-watchdog  </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>TimeoutSec，定义 Systemd 停止当前服务之前等待的秒数   - Environment，指定环境变量</p>\n</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<p><strong>使用服务</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#启动服务\nsystemctl start nginx\n#停止服务\nsystemctl stop nginx\n#开启自启动\nsystemctl enable nginx\n#关闭开启自启动\nsystemctl disable nginx</code></pre>\n\n\n\n","text":"nginx源码官网：nginx news 源码包： 下载想要的nginx版本 1.源码包下载： 复制源码包的下载链接 -P 指定下载包的路径 wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;nginx.org&#x2F;download&#x2F;nginx-x.x.x.tar.gz...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.4k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":6,"path":"api/categories/linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LNMP+N","slug":"LNMP-N","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LNMP-N.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-